subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
lead_paragraph: Kansas advanced despite the offensive struggles of Thomas Robinson, who had 11 points, and the hot shooting of Purdue’s Robbie Hummel, who had 26 points in his final game.
